details.name: HIT - T R O N
details.creator: -Hitokiri-
details.desc: Tron bike (Shotaro) performs the best, plus if you don't pick a Tron bike in a race that is called ''TRON'', why in the hell did you buy the most expensive bike in the game! Since it's a Tron themed race it's supposed to be played at night, so don't touch anything, if i set it at night you play it at night, i don't give a damn! Features new stunt elements such as; a double boosted lane & wall phasing.
